WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.599 --> 00:00:02.759
This is what a parent or athlete sees when

2
00:00:02.799 --> 00:00:03.980
they book a lesson with you.

3
00:00:04.619 --> 00:00:09.899
They land on your personal page, yourname.lessonspot.app.

4
00:00:10.579 --> 00:00:13.500
No app to download, no account to create, just

5
00:00:13.539 --> 00:00:16.859
